cy policies.\n*   **Other Hotels in Nahan (near Renuka Lake):** Nahan is the closest town to Renuka Lake and may offer more accommodation options. Check online travel platforms for hotels in Nahan with good reviews and inquire directly about their policies.\n\n**Safety and Precautions:**\n\n*   **Carry Valid Identification:** Always carry valid photo IDs (Aadhar card, passport, driver's license) for both individuals.\n*   **Be Respectful of Local Customs:** While attitudes are changing, some areas might still be conservative. Dress modestly when exploring outside the resort.\n*   **Avoid Public Displays of Affection:** Excessive public displays of affection might attract unwanted attention in some areas.\n*   **Trust Your Instincts:** If you feel uncomfortable or unsafe in any situation, remove yourself from it immediately.\n*   **Inform Someone of Your Travel Plans:** Share your itinerary and accommodation details with a trusted friend or family member.\n\n**Important Considerations:**\n\n*   **Moral Policing:** While less common in established tourist areas, the risk of moral policing cannot be entirely eliminated.\n*   **Hotel Policies:** Hotel policies can change, so always confirm the details before booking.\n*   **Local Laws:** Be aware of any local laws or regulations regarding unmarried couples staying together (though these are becoming increasingly rare).\n\n**Disclaimer:**\n\nI cannot guarantee that any specific resort will be completely free from potential issues. This information is based on general knowledge and online reviews, and it's essential to do your own research and make informed decisions.\n",
